name: Dark Knight Fashion
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:

https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi

DARK KNIGHT FASHION

Drifting beyond all time
Out of a churning sky
Drawn to the beckoning light
Of the dark eternal night

Trapped in a hellish dream
Spinning past worlds unseen
And frightfully vanishing
Into the dark eternal night

Darkness is calling, will you respond?

Download this LoRA and enter the night
